ntptr(sp) gp.sigcode1 = pc mcall(recovery) throw("recovery failed") // mcall should not return } } // ran out of deferred calls - old-school panic now // Because it is unsafe to call arbitrary user code after freezing // the world, we call preprintpanics to invoke all necessary Error // and String methods to prepare the panic strings before startpanic. preprintpanics(gp._panic) fatalpanic(gp._panic) // should not return *(*int)(nil) = 0 // not reached
